A RESOLUTION
1 Honoring the life and memory of Gene Ferguson; and for other purposes.
2 WHEREAS, the State of Georgia mourns the loss of one of its most distinguished citizens
3 with the passing of Gene Ferguson on March 3, 2025; and
4 WHEREAS, Gene Ferguson gave inspiration to many through his high ideals, morals, and
5 deep concern for his fellow citizens, and the devotion, patience, and understanding he
6 demonstrated to his family and friends were admired by others; and
7 WHEREAS, he was a person of magnanimous strengths with an unimpeachable reputation
8 for integrity, intelligence, fairness, and kindness, and by the example he made of his life, he
9 made this world a better place in which to live; and
10 WHEREAS, a compassionate and generous man, Gene Ferguson will long be remembered
11 for his love of family, friendship, and community and will be missed by all who had the great
12 fortune of knowing him.
